  <original-body>In master:

@@@ erb
&lt;%= render :text =&gt; 'Hello world!' %&gt;
@@@

produces no output. Likewise when you call `render :text` from a helper.

This example is contrived, but it seems like for consistency it should work.

My patch for #3260 includes a fix for this, but here's a new patch that isolates the fix and provides a test.</original-body>
